title: Cifford Fun With Dan Wardell | Iowa State Fair 2012

json.text: >> WHY IS EVERYBODY WAITING IN LINE HERE?
>> WHO ARE YOU WAITING IN LINE FOR? >> CLIFFORD.
>> WHO ARE YOU WAITING IN LINE FOR? >> CLIFFORD.
>> MOM, WHO ARE YOU WAITING IN LINE FOR? >> CLIFFORD.
>> OF COURSE SHE. ARE YOU READY TO SEE CLIFFORD?
>> YEAH!!! >> IT'S CLIFFORD!!!
>> CLIFFORD!!! >> FOR YEARS AND YEARS KIDS AND FAMILIES HAVE
COME TO THE VARIED INDUSTRY BUILDING TO SEE CLIFFORD THE BIG RED DOG.
ARE YOU GOING TO GIVE CLIFFORD A HUG OR A HIGH FIVE?
>> HUG. >> HIGH FIVE.
>> HIGH FIVE. GO FOR IT!
GO FOR IT! WATCH OUT, CLIFFORD,
THEY'RE COMING RIGHT IN FOR YOU. OHT, CLIFFORD IS GETTING MOBBED.
THERE'S A HUG. THERE'S A HIGH FIVE.
WOOO, THAT WAS A GOOD ONE. GO GIVE HIM A HIGH FIVE.
WOW, THERE'S A GOOD ONE. OH, A DOUBLE HIGH FIVE.
OH, SHE CHANGED HER MIND LAST MINUTE AND SHE WENT IN FOR THE HUG.
THAT'S A STEALTH NINJA MOVE. CLIFFORD NEVER GETS TIRED OF GET TIRED OF
HUGS. HE NEVER GETS TIRED OF
HIGH FIVES. AND EVEN DADS AND MOMS CAN COME GIVE CLIFFORD
A HUG. PEOPLE HAVE PHOTO ALBUMS OF PICTURES THROUGHOUT
THE YEARS OF FAMILIES GROWING UP AND COMING TO THE FAIR TO SEE CLIFFORD.
ALL RIGHT, CLIFFORD, YOU LOVE HIGH FIVES, RIGHT?
AND YOU LOVE HUGS TOO? WILL YOU HUG ANYBODY HERE?
WILL YOU EVEN HAVE A CAT? WILL YOU HUG ME, CLIFFORD?
OH, CLIFFORD! OH, HE'S SO CUTE!
HE'S FUZZY! HE'S REMARKABLY FUZZY.
I'LL PAT YOU ON THE NOSE TOO. GOOD JOB, BOY.
I KNOW WHAT YOU'RE THINKING: WHAT DOES IT FEEL LIKE WHEN YOU
GIVE A BIG DOG LIKE CLIFFORD A HUG? >> HE SO FUZZY AND SOFT.
>> HE DID FEEL FUZZY AND SOFT. GOOD JOB.
DID HE SHED ON YOU? DID HE GET ANY RED FUR ON YOU?
>> NO. >> OKAY, GOOD.
>> HAPPY. >> HAPPY.
>> NOW, IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE HE FELT LIKE? LIKE WITH YOUR FINGERS,
WHAT DID HE FEEL LIKE?
CLIFFORD IS HERE EVERY SINGLE DAY.
SO MANY PEOPLE HAVE SEEN HIM ALREADY, AND YOU STILL HAVE A FEW MORE CHANCES TO COME
OUT TO THE FAIR AND SEE CLIFFORD THE BIG RED DOG.
